.hide
	#linkingStarted
		| {{#if view.stateConnecting}}
		| Makin' pals with LinkedIn...
		i.icon-spinner.icon-spin.pull-right
		| {{/if}}
		| {{#if view.stateParsing}}
		div {{view.current}} of {{view.total}}
		.progress1.progress.progress-striped.active
			| <div class="bar" {{bindAttr style="view.percent"}}></div>
			.progress2.progress.active
				| <div class="bar" {{bindAttr style="view.percent2"}}></div>
		| {{/if}}
		| {{#if view.stateDone}}
		| Be patient while we update your connections.
		| {{/if}}
		| {{#if view.stateDoneAndDone}}
		| LinkedIn connections updated.
		| {{/if}}
		| {{#if view.stateThrottled}}
		| <br>That's enough for today:<br>come back and do some more tomorrow.
		| {{/if}}
